    {% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

        <h3>Too many links</h3>

        <p>Do not apply lots of links to paragraph text otherwise a user will have trouble reading the content in its entirety before making a selection.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-too-many-links.svg" alt="Example of best practice for too many links" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h3>Multiple link variants</h3>

        <p>Do not use multiple link variants to direct a user to the same destination.</p>

         {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-multiple-link-variants.svg" alt="Example of best practice for multiple link variants" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}
         <h3>Ambiguity</h3>

        <p>When writing link text, avoid ambiguous phrases or a full website URL. A user should have a clear idea of where they are being directed to before they make a selection.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-ambiguity.svg" alt="Example of best practice for Ambiguous links" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h3>Long links</h3>

        <p>Do not use either link variant with lots of text.</p>

         {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-long-links.svg" alt="Example of best practice for Long links" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}
         <h3>Buttons</h3>

        <p>Buttons have very different use cases than links and should not be used to promote offers or other content.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-buttons.svg" alt="Example of best practice for button links" style="--inline-img-max-width: 309px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        
         <h3>External link icon</h3>

        <p>Do not apply the external link icon to either Call to action link variant.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="/assets/link/best-practice-external-link-icon.svg" alt="Example of best practice for exsternal links" style="--inline-img-max-width: 406px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h3>Widows</h3>

        <p>The Default call to action variant link arrow and the external link icon should not appear by themselves, they should always be connected to at least one word on the same line.</p>

         {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
